title: Blossom Du Jour - Chelsea
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Kosher
description: Billed as "shrewd fast food," it's a fast food version of Blossom Restaurant and is the flagship locatio. Offers wraps, burgers, salads, raw pizza, raw burrito, soups, fresh juices, smoothies, and sweets. Operating since Oct 2010; previously 174 Ninth Ave, Midtown/Chelsea, next door to Cocoa V.
